Did You Catch That? The LUCKIEST Widowmaker Teleporter Shot
data.description: During Stage 4 of the 2019 Overwatch League, the London Spitfire pulled off a crazy play with Symmetra and Widowmaker on Blizzard World by using a Teleporter to secure a surprise first headshot against the Guangzhou Charge. But did you catch just HOW Profit got the shot past Guangzhou Charge’s shields? "Did You Catch That?" is an educational series that highlights exceptional moments in the Overwatch League that might have happened too quickly to catch! It’s all part of Insights: powered by Intel. Want more Insights? Visit https://overwatchleague.com/en-us/intel-insights.
